<i>noun</i>: 배치 [배치], 배치 [배ː치], 배속 [배ː속] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>배치 [배치]</dt><br>
<dd>arrangement; placement</dd><br>
<dd>사람이나 물건 등을 일정한 순서나 간격에 따라 벌여 놓음.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of placing persons, objects, etc., in a certain order or spacing.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>배치 [배ː치]</dt><br>
<dd>arrangement; placement</dd><br>
<dd>사람이나 물건 등을 알맞은 자리에 나누어 놓음.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of classifying and arranging persons, objects, etc., to a certain place.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>배속 [배ː속]</dt><br>
<dd>1. placement</dd><br>
<dd>물자를 어떤 곳에 배치하여 소속시킴.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of placing some supplies somewhere.</dd><br>
<dd>2. assignment</dd><br>
<dd>사람을 어떤 부서에 배치하여 그곳에서 일하게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of assigning a person to a department and making him/her work there.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>